{"tid":1459762,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(金融攬炒)請索羅斯出山再沽空港元有無得諗","createTime":"2019-08-12T20:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T03:19:05.000Z","uid":72431,"like":63,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a75e7631e7c6bd6c5a47a9b2602eabd1cc17e470","tid":1459762,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:09:33.000Z","msg":"email比wall street 各大金融大鱷<br />\n請求聯手沽空港元<br />\n唔好理係咪太天真 ,做左無壞<br />\n<br />\n1997:<br />\n更為港人所熟知的是，索羅斯是那個在97年帶來亞洲金融風暴，在98年狙擊港元的「金融大鱷」。在這場金融戰爭中，索羅斯以一人之力拖跨了泰國、馬來西亞、印尼、南韓等國家的貨幣和經濟，使這些國家陷入經濟衰退。而在與香港政府一戰中，剛成立的特區政府打下了為國際分析家津津樂道的「勝仗」，成功保衛聯繫匯率和擊退炒家"},{"pid":"13aebc48261b74fdf39fce40b34639813729355d","tid":1459762,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:10:07.000Z","msg":"sorry小妹借位跪求推<br />\n突發！ 點解冇人講816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1bc055c053fd70fda04d9d3aee455ff0ccce4d7f","tid":1459762,"uid":287792,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:16:40.000Z","msg":"中國有四大銀行"},{"pid":"6fc2127e1cded458d8e62b995da974fae0dedf49","tid":1459762,"uid":72431,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"1bc055c053fd70fda04d9d3aee455ff0ccce4d7f","tid":1459762,"uid":287792,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:16:40.000Z","msg":"中國有四大銀行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:23:11.000Z","msg":"佢咪出手頂囉<br />\n睇佢睇到幾多<br />\n全球一齊沽爆"},{"pid":"2ba2f548dc69b5a940d22a3f1dc7c01bdbc72761","tid":1459762,"uid":247330,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:42:20.000Z","msg":"俾香港人㩒走美元先叫佢出手"},{"pid":"feaa9d7986ef6aab46a80d9a5dd7609414a9e6d4","tid":1459762,"uid":108814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ba2f548dc69b5a940d22a3f1dc7c01bdbc72761","tid":1459762,"uid":247330,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:42:20.000Z","msg":"俾香港人㩒走美元先叫佢出手